          <p><em>From <a href="https://code.google.com/u/109067824594513388759/">thilo.mu...@gmail.com</a> on March 18, 2012 06:35:53</em></p>

<p>This feature will not be included in the upcoming 0.3.0 release, but it is definitely not forgotten. Implementing it is not a trivial task as we have to extend the feature set of the render-theme API as well as the underlying map renderer.</p>

<p><strong>Cc:</strong> <a href="mailto:-jjbross@gmail.com">-jjbross@gmail.com</a>  </p>
